Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which features the women in Rome, the "Bravo, Bravo, f*cking Bravo" moment, and a supernatural presence. On The Real Housewives of New York, the cast arrives in Mexico, where Sonja has too much coke and rosé, and Leah and Ramona butt heads.


RHONY Recap: 33:37ish
